Pick up the credit card.
Turn right and walk to the garbage then turn left and walk past the cardboard box that's on the ledge to your right then turn left and walk to the first silver chair and turn to face it.
Put the credit card on the cushion in the bottom left corner.
Turn left and walk to the chair then turn left and take a step left so you're looking at a couch with a credit card on it's cushion.
Pick up the credit card.
Go back to where you put the first credit card.
Put this one to the right of the other credit card about three credit card width's away.

grab the credit card off of the table

place the credit card down on the chair there

grab the credit card off of the sofa there
walk back over to the grey chair you put the other credit card on on your right
place the credit card down on the grey chair
